---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 522
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=Help Through Prayer
By: Ibn 'Atâ’illâh
---
Prayer is a cleansing for hearts from the stain of iniquities, and an
opening to the door of the Mysteries.

Prayer is the place of confidences and the wellspring of intimacies：
in it widens the scope of the Mysteries, and in it shine the rays of
the Luminaries.
